(249, 31, '关于Mingshop 隐藏index.php 一问题', '<p>有些朋友提到关于Mingshop 隐藏index.php 一问题， 可以修改 Application\\Common\\Conf\\config.php 文件代码 <br/></p><pre class="brush:php;toolbar:false">&#39;common&#39;,\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;AUTH_CODE&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&quot;TPSHOP&quot;,&nbsp;//安装完毕之后不要改变，否则所有密码都会出错\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&#39;URL_CASE_INSENSITIVE&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;false,&nbsp;//URL大小写不敏感\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;LOAD_EXT_CONFIG&#39;=&gt;&#39;db,route&#39;,&nbsp;//&nbsp;加载数据库配置文件\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;LOAD_EXT_CONFIG&#39;=&gt;&#39;db&#39;,&nbsp;//&nbsp;加载数据库配置文件\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;URL_MODEL&#39;=&gt;2,&nbsp;//&nbsp;如果需要&nbsp;隐藏&nbsp;index.php&nbsp;&nbsp;打开这行&quot;URL_MODEL&quot;注释&nbsp;同时在apache环境下&nbsp;开启&nbsp;伪静态模块，&nbsp;&nbsp;如果在nginx&nbsp;下需要另外配置，参考thinkphp官网手册</pre><p><br/></p><p>有些环境刚修改上面还是不行，需要另外修改根目录下的 .htaccess&nbsp; 文件&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><pre class="brush:php;toolbar:false">&nbsp;&nbsp;Options&nbsp;+FollowSymlinks\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;RewriteEngine&nbsp;On\r\n\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;RewriteCond&nbsp;%{REQUEST_FILENAME}&nbsp;!-d\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;RewriteCond&nbsp;%{REQUEST_FILENAME}&nbsp;!-f\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;#RewriteRule&nbsp;^(.*)$&nbsp;index.php/$1&nbsp;[QSA,PT,L]&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;RewriteRule&nbsp;^(.*)$&nbsp;index.php?s=$1&nbsp;[QSA,PT,L]</pre><p>原来的<br/></p><p>&nbsp;RewriteRule ^(.*)$ index.php/$1 [QSA,PT,L]&nbsp; <br/></p><p>改成<br/></p><p>&nbsp;RewriteRule ^(.*)$ index.php?s=$1 [QSA,PT,L]&nbsp; <br/></p><p>重启apache&nbsp; 试试。</p><p><br/></p><p>对于nginx 用户 请查看thinkphp 官网手册说明<br/></p>', '', '', '', 2, 1, 1465055906, '', 0, '', '', 1405, 1465056000, ''),
(250, 10, 'Mingshop隐藏index.php', '<p>有些朋友提到关于Mingshop 隐藏index.php 一问题， 可以修改 Application\\Common\\Conf\\config.php 文件代码 <br/></p><pre class="brush:php;toolbar:false">&#39;common&#39;,\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;AUTH_CODE&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&quot;TPSHOP&quot;,&nbsp;//安装完毕之后不要改变，否则所有密码都会出错\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&#39;URL_CASE_INSENSITIVE&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;false,&nbsp;//URL大小写不敏感\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;LOAD_EXT_CONFIG&#39;=&gt;&#39;db,route&#39;,&nbsp;//&nbsp;加载数据库配置文件\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;LOAD_EXT_CONFIG&#39;=&gt;&#39;db&#39;,&nbsp;//&nbsp;加载数据库配置文件\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;URL_MODEL&#39;=&gt;2,&nbsp;//&nbsp;如果需要&nbsp;隐藏&nbsp;index.php&nbsp;&nbsp;打开这行&quot;URL_MODEL&quot;注释&nbsp;同时在apache环境下&nbsp;开启&nbsp;伪静态模块，&nbsp;&nbsp;如果在nginx&nbsp;下需要另外配置，参考thinkphp官网手册</pre><p><br/></p><p>有些环境刚修改上面还是不行，需要另外修改根目录下的 .htaccess&nbsp; 文件&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><pre class="brush:php;toolbar:false">&nbsp;&nbsp;Options&nbsp;+FollowSymlinks\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;RewriteEngine&nbsp;On\r\n\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;RewriteCond&nbsp;%{REQUEST_FILENAME}&nbsp;!-d\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;RewriteCond&nbsp;%{REQUEST_FILENAME}&nbsp;!-f\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;#RewriteRule&nbsp;^(.*)$&nbsp;index.php/$1&nbsp;[QSA,PT,L]&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;RewriteRule&nbsp;^(.*)$&nbsp;index.php?s=$1&nbsp;[QSA,PT,L]</pre><p>原来的<br/></p><p>&nbsp;RewriteRule ^(.*)$ index.php/$1 [QSA,PT,L]&nbsp; <br/></p><p>改成<br/></p><p>&nbsp;RewriteRule ^(.*)$ index.php?s=$1 [QSA,PT,L]&nbsp; <br/></p><p>重启apache&nbsp; 试试。</p><p><br/></p><p>对于nginx 用户 请查看thinkphp 官网手册说明<br/></p>', '', '', '', 2, 1, 1465056409, '', 0, '', '', 1214, 1465056000, ''),
(251, 53, 'v1.2.3 升级记录', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;Mingshop V1.3 主要调试了 手机APP 接口. 同时发布 APP端 原生态 IOS版,&amp;nbsp; 手机端API接口 . 详细见官网手册.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;手机端API 接口 模块位于 Application\\Api\\Controller&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;另外 Mingshop&amp;nbsp; 多商家版 +微信三级分销&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; 也在近日内即将发布.&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; 以下是 1.3 的升级记录所修改的文件&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;brush:php;toolbar:false&quot;&gt;升级将覆盖如下文件,&amp;nbsp;如果做了二次开发,&amp;nbsp;请先备份如下文件\r\n/Install/index.php\r\n/Install/templates/step3.php\r\n/Application/Index/Controller/ArticleController.class.php\r\n/Application/Api/Controller/BaseController.class.php\r\n/Application/Admin/View/System/basic.html\r\n/Application/Common/Common/common.php\r\n/Template/pc/mingshop/Index/download.html\r\n/Template/pc/mingshop/Index/fw.html\r\n/Template/pc/default/Static/js/jquery.jqzoom.js\r\n/Template/pc/default/Activity/group.html\r\n/Template/pc/default/Goods/goodsInfo.html\r\n/Application/Api/Controller/GoodsController.class.php\r\n/Template/pc/default/Public/header.html\r\n/Template/pc/default/Static/css/index.css\r\n/Template/pc/default/Static/css/jqzoom.css\r\n/Application/Api/Controller/UserController.class.php\r\n/Application/Home/Logic/UsersLogic.class.php\r\n/Template/mobile/new/User/add_address.html\r\n/Template/mobile/new/User/edit_address.html\r\n/Application/Home/Controller/WeixinController.class.php\r\n/Application/Admin/View/Goods/_goods.html\r\n/Application/Common/Conf/config.php\r\n/Application/Home/Controller/GoodsController.class.php\r\n/Template/pc/soubao/Static/images/csmrrvbluacaoflbaacb1akwoks248.jpg\r\n/Template/pc/mingshop/Public/header.html\r\n/plugins/login/alipay/lib/alipay_core.function.php\r\n/Template/pc/mingshop/Index/index.html\r\n/Template/pc/mingshop/Index/images